Package controllers

Class SubscriberStatusController

java.lang.Object
controllers.SubscriberStatusController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientAware
public class SubscriberStatusController extends Object implements ClientAware
This controller handles the Subscriber Status report screen. It lets the user pick a month and year, sends a request to the server, and shows the data in a table, a bar chart, and a pie chart.
